 2023-07812023-07-26PMO
ActCanada Small Business Financing Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Small Business and Tourism as the Minister for the Purposes of the Canada Small Business Financing Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2021-939 of October 26, 2021; and (2) designating the Minister of SMALL BUSINESS AND TOURISM, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the CANADA SMALL BUSINESS FINANCING ACT.
